'''
Test tool interrupt with parameter modification - explore v2 block
This script tests parameter modification in explore block v2.
The LLM will call high_risk_tool, user can modify parameters during interrupt.

Available tools:
- high_risk_tool: Requires confirmation (param: string)
- safe_tool: Safe operation, no confirmation needed (param: string)
''' -> system_prompt

'''
Task: Call high_risk_tool with param="original_value".
After the operation completes, summarize the result.
''' -> query_explore

/explore/(
    tools=["high_risk_tool", "safe_tool"],
    system_prompt=$system_prompt
) $query_explore -> explore_result

'''Final result: {explore_result}''' -> final_result

